msgid "Install MSYS2"
msgstr "Instalați MSYS2"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../troubleshoot.rst:58
msgid ""
"The Windows version of OpenShot is compiled using an environment called "
"MSYS2. In order to attach the GDB debugger to our executable, ``openshot-qt."
"exe``, you must first install MSYS2. This step is only required once."
